element.text: Welcome to Western Digital Partner Summit organized exclusively for Partners like you. We bring you our entire range of products, live sessions, industry updates, engagements and more in this one-of-its-kind virtual summit, just a click away. Come! Explore the world of data organized with absolute finesse to give you an enriching experience.

Various activities you participate in this summit will give you a chance to earn points. Find the number of points you have scored so far on the leader board and ensure that you are on the top of the list to stand a chance to win exciting prizes.
